newsitem.title: NETHERLANDS: European feeds remain dull in afternoon.
newsitem.headline: European feeds remain dull in afternoon.

text.p: Business on the European meals and feeds market remained dull this afternoon with only three trades reported, market sources said.
"There was little buying mood today and calls for a weaker Chicago soymeal opening coupled to a stronger dollar also kept a firm lid on activity," one broker said.

Arrived Brazilian soymeal pellets traded at $289 a tonne cif Rotterdam, Oct/Dec citruspulp pellets changed hands at $119 a tonne cif and EU rapemeal traded at 28 marks per 100 kg fob lower Rhine.--KAREL LUIMES +31 20 504 5832
